title: E! Orders Second Season of Caitlyn Jenner's "I Am Cait"
text:
E! Orders Second Season of Caitlyn Jenner's "I Am Cait" Posted just a moment ago 
ESPYs (LOS ANGELES) -- Caitlyn Jenner will continue to document her life as a transgender woman for E! 
The cable network has renewed Jenner's series, I Am Cait , for a second season. The new episodes will premiere in 2016. 
“I’m looking forward to continuing the conversation,” Jenner said in a statement. 
Season one premiered in late July, nearly two months after Jenner debuted her current name and look on the cover of Vanity Fair . The season featured eight episodes.
